name: 杰瑞德·莫泽
introduction: Jared Moser is a professional actor and entrepreneur. Moser began his career in Kansas City Missouri by taking classes with Dan Shirley, Andy Garrison, and Bill Dance. Moser started in several small films and commercials in Kansas City before eventually moving to Los Angeles as the age of 19. While in LA, Moser worked at his personal startup company called Joltek LLC which is still in business today. Moser was eventually contracted through Central Casting and started in several background roles to include Pretty Little Liars, Transformers: Dark of the Moon, and Fast Five. Moser is currently enlisted in the United States Air Force as an Air Traffic Controller. His most recent appearances include his personal YouTube channel which has accumulated over One Million Views. In a recent interview in 2015, Moser states he plans to re enter the acting world and eventually star in a main role feature film.
